<h1>Booking Confirmed</h1>

<p>Hi <%= @guest.first_name || @guest.email.split("@").first %>,</p>

<p>Your booking is confirmed. Here are the details:</p>

<div class="detail-box">
  <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="font-size: 14px;">
    <tr>
      <td style="padding: 6px 0; color: #6b7280;">Property</td>
      <td style="padding: 6px 0; color: #111c2d; font-weight: 600; text-align: right;"><%= @property.title %></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="padding: 6px 0; color: #6b7280;">Location</td>
      <td style="padding: 6px 0; color: #111c2d; font-weight: 600; text-align: right;"><%= @property.city %>, <%= @property.country %></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="padding: 6px 0; color: #6b7280;">Check-in</td>
      <td style="padding: 6px 0; color: #111c2d; font-weight: 600; text-align: right;"><%= @booking.check_in.strftime("%A, %d %B %Y") %></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="padding: 6px 0; color: #6b7280;">Check-out</td>
      <td style="padding: 6px 0; color: #111c2d; font-weight: 600; text-align: right;"><%= @booking.check_out.strftime("%A, %d %B %Y") %></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="padding: 6px 0; color: #6b7280;">Nights</td>
      <td style="padding: 6px 0; color: #111c2d; font-weight: 600; text-align: right;"><%= @booking.nights %></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="padding: 6px 0; color: #6b7280;">Guests</td>
      <td style="padding: 6px 0; color: #111c2d; font-weight: 600; text-align: right;"><%= @booking.guests_count %></td>
    </tr>
    <tr style="border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">
      <td style="padding: 10px 0 6px; color: #111c2d; font-weight: 700;">Total</td>
      <td style="padding: 10px 0 6px; color: #111c2d; font-weight: 700; text-align: right; font-size: 16px;">&euro;<%= number_with_delimiter(@booking.total_price, delimiter: ",") %></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="padding: 4px 0; color: #6b7280; font-size: 12px;">Invoice Reference</td>
      <td style="padding: 4px 0; color: #6b7280; font-family: monospace; text-align: right; font-size: 12px;"><%= @booking.invoice_reference %></td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</div>

<p>Your host will be in touch with check-in details. If you need anything, you can message them directly through WorkStays.</p>

<p style="text-align: center; margin: 24px 0;">
  <a href="<%= booking_url(@booking) %>" class="btn">View Booking</a>
</p>

<p>Thanks for using WorkStays.</p>
